posts.post_title: looking for low grade1911 t205 gold borders
posts.post_content: Right now I'm trying to start collecting t205 gold borders. I'm looking for low grades and I would be fine with commons or stars. I don't have any cards from that era, but I have a lot of big names from 1948 to 1977 to trade for. Just let me know what cards you have and let's trade.
